    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "引言：为什么研究现实情境中的分类",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300054384_3_554-646",
          "range": "554-646",
          "rangeStart": 554,
          "rangeEnd": 646,
          "markText": "想要将某个人归入某一类别（朋友或敌人；值得信任或不值得信任）是人类与生俱来的天性，这种渴求为智力发展提供了基础。如果我们不去构成类别，我们就只能注意到个例，而触及不到任何总体性的思考。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1742200497,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-03-17 16:34:57",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054384&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=646",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44132240813ab7bbeg01417c?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=646"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300054384_3_386-414",
          "range": "386-414",
          "rangeStart": 386,
          "rangeEnd": 414,
          "markText": "对确定性的需求是人类的天性，然而，这也是人类智慧的缺点。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1742200484,
